---
title: Tourongo — Payment & Payout Flow
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Traveler
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Spring Boot
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant STRIPE as Stripe
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant GW as Guide Wallet

    Note over T,GW: Phase 1 — Booking & Payment

    T->>FE: Click "Book Now" + agree waiver
    FE->>API: POST /api/traveler/bookings
    API->>DB: SELECT ... FOR UPDATE (occurrence lock, 2000ms timeout)
    DB-->>API: Lock acquired
    API->>DB: Check seatsReserved + peopleCount ≤ maxCapacity
    API->>DB: seatsReserved += peopleCount
    API->>DB: INSERT booking (PendingPayment, cartExpiresAt=now+15min, qrCode=UUID)
    API->>DB: COMMIT (lock released)
    API-->>FE: BookingResponse (bookingId, cartExpiresAtUtc)
    FE->>FE: Start PaymentCountdownBanner (usePaymentCountdown hook)

    T->>FE: Click "Pay Now"
    FE->>API: POST /api/payments/create-session (bookingId)
    API->>STRIPE: Create Checkout Session
    STRIPE-->>API: {sessionId, checkoutUrl}
    API-->>FE: {sessionId, checkoutUrl}
    FE->>STRIPE: Redirect to Stripe Checkout

    alt Payment Success
        STRIPE->>API: POST /api/payments/webhook (checkout.session.completed)
        Note over API: stripe-signature header verified
        API->>DB: UPDATE booking SET status=Confirmed, cartExpiresAt=NULL
        API->>DB: UPDATE payment SET status=Captured, paidAt=now
        API->>DB: SET payoutEligibleAt = now + freeze-hours
        API->>WS: PAYMENT_SUCCESS → /topic/notifications/{travelerId}
        API->>WS: BOOKING_CREATED → /topic/notifications/{guideId}
        STRIPE-->>FE: Redirect /bookings/{id}?success=true
    else Timeout (15 min elapsed, no payment)
        Note over API,DB: PaymentTimeoutJob polls every 60s
        API->>DB: UPDATE booking SET status=Expired
        API->>DB: seatsReserved -= peopleCount
        API->>DB: Promote next WAITING waitlist entry (if any)
        API->>WS: BOOKING_EXPIRED → /topic/notifications/{travelerId}
        API->>WS: BOOKING_CANCELLED → /topic/notifications/{guideId}
    end

    Note over T,GW: Phase 2 — Tour Execution & Escrow Release

    T->>API: Show QR code (from booking ticket page)
    API->>FE: QR renders 1h before tour start
    FE->>FE: html5-qrcode scanner (guide's on-tour page)
    FE->>API: POST /guide/bookings/checkin-by-qr/{qrToken}
    API->>DB: UPDATE booking SET status=InProgress, checkedInAt=now
    API->>WS: Notify traveler: tour started

    FE->>API: POST /guide/bookings/{id}/complete
    API->>DB: UPDATE booking SET status=Completed, completedAt=now
    API->>DB: UPDATE payment SET payoutEligibleAt = completedAt + freeze-hours
    API->>DB: travelerProfile.completedBookingCount++
    API->>DB: Recalculate loyalty tier (BRONZE→SILVER→GOLD)

    Note over API,GW: PayoutReleaseJob runs hourly
    API->>DB: Find payments WHERE payoutStatus=Pending AND payoutEligibleAt <= now
    API->>STRIPE: Transfer (netAmount) to guide.stripeConnectAccountId
    STRIPE-->>API: Transfer confirmed (stripeTransferId)
    API->>DB: UPDATE payment SET payoutStatus=Transferred, stripeTransferId=...
    API->>WS: PAYOUT_PROCESSED → /topic/notifications/{guideId}
    DB-->>GW: Earnings appear in guide wallet
